---
title: Smoky Barramundi with Remoulade with Green Bean Cabbage Slaw
description: Nuanced flavours star in this seafood-centric dish. Barramundi seasoned with a smoky BBQ seasoning is pan-seared, then finished in the oven. Sautéed green beans and a tangy cabbage, apple, and cranberry slaw round out this fresh and fun dish, with a kick from the horseradish rémoulade sauce adding a final pop!

